## Proposed Changes

### 1. Presentation Settings — Font Size Range
Expand the font size range in the typography dialog up to 300 (formerly capped at 100) and clamp the text box inputs.

#### [MODIFY] [presentation_settings_dialog.dart](file:///c:/Users/bhanu/projects/KeryxPro/lib/features/settings/presentation/widgets/presentation_settings_dialog.dart)
- Inside `_showTypographyDialog`:
  - Update the list box generator from `List.generate(96, (i) => i + 5)` to `List.generate(296, (i) => i + 5)` to include items from 5 up to 300.
  - In the `TextField`'s `onChanged` handler for the size input:
    - Parse the value and, if it exceeds `300.0`, clamp it to `300.0`.
    - Update the text controller text to `300` and place the selection cursor at the end to visually enforce the clamp on change.

