Introduce providers to track the pin mode, visibility, active tab, and tab controller of the Monitor pane.

#### [MODIFY] [global_ui_providers.dart](file:///c:/Users/bhanu/projects/KeryxPro/lib/features/dashboard/presentation/global_ui_providers.dart)
